    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>"Zend_Pagiinator_Adapter_DbSelect" function count() needs to also reset the ORDER clause because COLUMNS resets, therefor if you rename a column with AS,  the ORDER BY clause will not see the column created with AS in the select statement.</p>

<p>I solved this problem by adding: reset(Zend_Db_Select::ORDER) after line 134.</p>

